releases.name: v1.5.0
releases.body:
### Changes
- Add: Auto launch at startup of computer

### Known problems
- A bundled auto updater is experimental. 

### Tested Environments
- --Windows 7 Home Premium x86_64--
- GNU/Linux 4.2.1 x86_64 (Arch Linux)

Thanks for tester members of Visual Media Lab :)

[NOTE] We does not provide the executable binary for Linux x86_32 (IA-32); If you need it, you can build it by yourself.

### Installation Guide
- Linux: https://github.com/odentools/odenwlan-node/wiki/InstallationOnLinux
- Windows: https://github.com/odentools/odenwlan-node/wiki/InstallationOnWindows

releases.name: v1.2.0
releases.body:
自動更新の実装とログインチェックの改良を行った試食版です。

### CHANGES
- New: Auto update (veryyyyy experimental function)
- Fix: Improved online checker
- Fix: Fixed a malfunction in post processing of login

### CAUTION for installation on Windows
- We recommends to deploy an unzipped file to the root folder, and that folder path should as short as possible. e.g. C:\odenwlan\ 
- DON'T to include the multi-byte string (e.g. Japanese character) in the folder path.

releases.name: v1.1.0
releases.body:
Second release version (experimental)

### CHANGES
- New function: Login manually when the tray icon was clicked
- Reduced archive size
- Improved retry processing
- Improved status check process

### CAUTION for installation on Windows
- We recommends to deploy an unzipped file to the root folder, and that folder path should as short as possible. e.g. C:\odenwlan\ 
- DON'T to include the multi-byte string (e.g. Japanese character) in the folder path.
